messages.text: Take care of this for me:)
no...who is this, i dont have ur #
wha??? jus tell me who u r! lol.
Just do as I say. Check your bank account.
Are you looking at your account?
hold on, let me pull it up
it is isnt it!! payback huh!!??
You can consider me a friend.
no really, who r u?? is this for real
I just need you to keep it safe for me.
Don't spend all of it though:)
You see. I'm in this predicament.
I need somewhere to keep this... borrowed money...
how did u get my account number??
I've watched you for several days now.
I don't intend to harm you.
There is no problem. See, I kinda like you.
I've gotten to know you over these past few days and you're a good girl.
this seriously is creeping me the freak out...
really, wats ur name?? Cory or sydney, ik its gotta be one of u guys
Sorry, I let my emotions get the best of me there.
Let me simply state that if it were one of them, how would you then explain the million dollars placed in your account.
They could not have done that.
You're cute you know that. Cute but not smart.
ur so weird and creepy... jus leave me alone!!!
I'm sorry you have to be a pawn in all of this, but you're just too perfect.
tell me who u r right now or im callin the cops!!
No no no no, please don't do that.
y is this money in my account??
Know of the Wilson Bank robbery?
Don't even keep up with the news do you...?
But basically we virtually robbed this bank and deposited the money into your account.
k, so y put it n my account??
No will suspect you have the money.
They're suspecting cyber nerds, not a 15 year old high school girl.
wat if they somehow track it?!
but like u said, how will they believe it?? theyll know I was setup.
Ah. But the proof is in your account. Hard to deny.
For all you know, you could be a cyber genius.
no way. seen my com. science scores??
Straight 100s. Guess you are a genius.
We just robbed a bank. We can do anything.
wat am i supposed to do now? walk around knowing there's a million dollars in my account??
i cant stand by and let this happen!!
I'm warning you, don't do it!
Thanks for holding on to it for a little bit :)
We were gonna just keep it there till everything dies down, maybe even given you a cut.
You'll get arrested, go to jail for a long time.
Which will be erased by the time they get here.
there's no way theyll believe this
Like I said: evidence. Btw the money is gone now. Shame. Bye bye.
And a letter on your laptop saying you took the money out and hid it but will never tell.
u wont get away with this!!!
